{
  "id": "RAW_a62dcd11",
  "title": "任何人都能构建智能体，但运行它们需要一个平台 - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/blog/anyone-can-build-agents-but-it-takes-a-platform-to-run-them",
  "date": "2026-02-09 13:00:00",
  "author": "Eric Dodds, Jeanne Grosser",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Prototyping is democratized, but production deployment isn't.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">AI models have commoditized code and agent generation, making it possible for anyone to build sophisticated software in minutes. Claude can scaffold a fully functional agent before your morning coffee gets cold. But that same AI will happily architect a $5,000/month DevOps setup when the system could run efficiently at $500/month.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">In a world where anyone can build internal tools and agents, the build vs. buy equation has fundamentally changed. Competitive advantage no longer comes from whether you can build. It comes from rapid iteration on AI that solves real problems for your business and, more importantly, reliably operating those systems at scale.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">To do that, companies need an internal AI stack as robust as their external product infrastructure. That's exactly what Vercel's agent orchestration platform provides.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"Building agents is becoming easier, but running them reliably requires robust production operations underneath.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"269\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__desktop rounded-md blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5BEHvpb4pAWevWptpq6Mwh%2Fc252a66230dde30a8b74a33da1e17385%2FAgent_light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5BEHvpb4pAWevWptpq6Mwh%2Fc252a66230dde30a8b74a33da1e17385%2FAgent_light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5BEHvpb4pAWevWptpq6Mwh%2Fc252a66230dde30a8b74a33da1e17385%2FAgent_light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"Building agents is becoming easier, but running them reliably requires robust production operations underneath.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"1126\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__mobile blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6H6oWC2GrgSQ6tsKV0A2FI%2F4f60ab4933f75b2a33de4a2fc5796f10%2FAgent_light_ml.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6H6oWC2GrgSQ6tsKV0A2FI%2F4f60ab4933f75b2a33de4a2fc5796f10%2FAgent_light_ml.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6H6oWC2GrgSQ6tsKV0A2FI%2F4f60ab4933f75b2a33de4a2fc5796f10%2FAgent_light_ml.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n    <figcaption class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 text-center m-auto max-w-[var(--article-max-width)] max-[600px]:px-0 max-[600px]:py-4\">Building agents is becoming easier, but running them reliably requires robust production operations underneath.</figcaption>\n   </div>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#build-vs.-buy-roi-has-fundamentally-changed\" id=\"build-vs.-buy-roi-has-fundamentally-changed\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Build vs. buy ROI has fundamentally changed</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">For decades, the economics of custom internal tools only made sense at large-scale companies. The upfront engineering investment was high, but the real cost was long-term operation with high SLAs and measurable ROI. For everyone else, buying off-the-shelf software was the practical option.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">AI has fundamentally changed this equation. Companies of any size can now create agents quickly, and customization delivers immediate ROI for specialized workflows:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">OpenAI deployed an <a href=\"https://openai.com/index/inside-our-in-house-data-agent/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://openai.com/index/inside-our-in-house-data-agent/\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">internal data agent</a> to democratize analytics</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Vercel’s <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/ai-agent-entry-level-sales-jobs-vercel-2025-10\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/ai-agent-entry-level-sales-jobs-vercel-2025-10\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">lead qualification agent</a> helps one SDR do the work of 10 (template <a href=\"https://vercel.com/templates/ai/lead-processing-agent\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/templates/ai/lead-processing-agent\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">here</a>)</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Stripe built a <a target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/blog/how-stripe-built-a-game-changing-app-in-a-single-flight-with-v0\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\" href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/how-stripe-built-a-game-changing-app-in-a-single-flight-with-v0\">customer-facing financial impact calculator</a> (on a flight!)</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Today the question isn’t build vs. buy. The answer is build <i>and run</i>. Instead of separating internal systems and vendors, companies need a single platform that can handle the unique demands of agent workloads.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-16 lg:text-heading-20 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-6 text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#every-company-needs-an-internal-ai-stack\" id=\"every-company-needs-an-internal-ai-stack\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Every company needs an internal AI stack</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">The number of use cases for internal apps and agents is exploding, but here's the problem: production is still hard.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Vibe coding has created one of the largest shadow IT problems in history, and understanding production operations requires expertise in security, observability, reliability, and cost optimization. These skills remain rare even as building becomes easier.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">The ultimate challenge for agents isn't building them, it's the platform they run on.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#the-platform-is-the-product:-how-our-data-agent-runs-on-vercel\" id=\"the-platform-is-the-product:-how-our-data-agent-runs-on-vercel\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>The platform is the product: how our data agent runs on Vercel</h2>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"d0 uses Vercel's agent orchestration platform to answer hundreds of questions per day, reliably and securely.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"371\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__desktop rounded-md blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2FXH6c51MbzUibxqrB9z3lQ%2Fde7c21ed107b2da8661e588a707608ae%2Fd0_light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2FXH6c51MbzUibxqrB9z3lQ%2Fde7c21ed107b2da8661e588a707608ae%2Fd0_light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2FXH6c51MbzUibxqrB9z3lQ%2Fde7c21ed107b2da8661e588a707608ae%2Fd0_light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"d0 uses Vercel's agent orchestration platform to answer hundreds of questions per day, reliably and securely.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"2000\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__mobile blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6UjCP9BACu1W3TdoZumvlM%2F44f65ecfe9348afc09ebdc899c24a436%2Fd0_light_ml.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6UjCP9BACu1W3TdoZumvlM%2F44f65ecfe9348afc09ebdc899c24a436%2Fd0_light_ml.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6UjCP9BACu1W3TdoZumvlM%2F44f65ecfe9348afc09ebdc899c24a436%2Fd0_light_ml.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n    <figcaption class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 text-center m-auto max-w-[var(--article-max-width)] max-[600px]:px-0 max-[600px]:py-4\">d0 uses Vercel's agent orchestration platform to answer hundreds of questions per day, reliably and securely.</figcaption>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Like OpenAI, we built our own internal data agent named <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span> (OSS template <a href=\"https://vercel.com/templates/ai/oss-data-analyst-agent-reference-architecture\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/templates/ai/oss-data-analyst-agent-reference-architecture\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">here</a>). At its core, <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span> is a text-to-SQL engine, which is not a new concept. What made it a successful product was the platform underneath.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Using Vercel’s built-in primitives and deployment infrastructure, one person built <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span> in a few weeks using 20% of their time.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">This was only possible because Sandboxes, Fluid compute and AI Gateway automatically handled the operational complexity that would have normally taken months of engineering effort to scaffold and secure.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Today, <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span> has completely democratized data access that was previously limited to professional analysts. Engineers, marketers, and executives can all ask questions in natural language and get immediate, accurate answers from our data warehouse.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Here’s how it works:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>A user asks a question in Slack: </b>\"What was our Enterprise ARR last quarter?\" <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span> receives the message, determines the right level of data access based on the permissions of the user, and starts the agent workflow.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>The agent explores a semantic layer: </b>The semantic layer is a file system of 5 layers of YAML-based configs that describe our data warehouse, our metrics, our products, and our operations.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>AI SDK handles the model calls: </b>Streaming responses, tool use, and structured outputs all work out of the box. We didn't build custom LLM plumbing, we used the same abstractions any Vercel developer can use.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Agent steps are orchestrated durably: </b>If a step fails (Snowflake timeout, model hiccup), Vercel Workflows handles retries and state recovery automatically.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Automated actions are executed in isolation</b>: File exploration, SQL generation, and query execution all happen in a secure Vercel Sandbox. Runaway operations can't escape, and the agent can execute arbitrary Python for advanced analysis.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Multiple models are used to balance cost and accuracy</b>: AI Gateway routes simple requests to fast models and complex analysis to Claude Opus, all in one code base.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>The answer arrives in Slack:</b> formatted results, often with a chart or Google Sheet link, are delivered back to the Slack using the AI SDK Chatbot primitive.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#vercel-is-the-platform-for-agents\" id=\"vercel-is-the-platform-for-agents\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Vercel is the platform for agents</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Vercel provides the infrastructure primitives purpose-built for agent workloads, both internal and customer-facing. You build the agent, Vercel runs it. And it just works.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Using our own agent orchestration platform has enabled us to build and manage an increasing number of custom agents.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Internally, we run:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">A lead qualification agent</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span>, our analytics agent</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">A customer support agent (that reduced tickets by a third),</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">An abuse detection agent that flags risky content</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">A content agent that turns Slack threads into draft blog posts.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">On the product side:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">v0</span> is a code generation agent, and</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Vercel Agent can review pull requests, analyze incidents, and recommend actions.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Both products run on the same primitives as our internal tools.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Sandboxes</b></a> give agents a secure, isolated environment for executing sensitive autonomous actions. This is critical for protecting your core systems. When agents generate and run untested code or face prompt injection attacks, sandboxes contain the damage within isolated Linux VMs. When agents need filesystem access for information discovery, sandboxes can dynamically mount VMs with secure access to the right resources.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-tsx code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> </span><span class=\"token imports maybe-class-name\">Sandbox</span><span class=\"token imports\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'@vercel/sandbox'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sandbox </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Sandbox</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sandbox</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">runCommand</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  cmd</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'node'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  args</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"-e\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'console.log(\"Hello from Vercel Sandbox!\")'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  stdout</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> process</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">stdout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C65e87f65-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sandbox</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">stop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/fluid-compute\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/fluid-compute\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Fluid compute</b></a>&nbsp;automatically handles the unpredictable, long-running compute patterns that agents create. It’s easy to ignore compute when agents are processing text, but when usage scales and you add data-heavy workloads for files, images, and video, cost becomes an issue quickly. Fluid compute automatically scales up and down based on demand, and you're only charged for compute time, keeping costs low and predictable.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"239\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__desktop rounded-md blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F1PoOxG1UDe7YStoAfDZFoO%2Fd5f488815adb649dd7d61343f8b208c5%2FFluid_compute_-_Light_-_Desktop.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F1PoOxG1UDe7YStoAfDZFoO%2Fd5f488815adb649dd7d61343f8b208c5%2FFluid_compute_-_Light_-_Desktop.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F1PoOxG1UDe7YStoAfDZFoO%2Fd5f488815adb649dd7d61343f8b208c5%2FFluid_compute_-_Light_-_Desktop.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n    <br>\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"461\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__mobile blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F703uGE86SPESaiHPigCGmy%2F5cc98e8b1ab7f04b9013e44fd8251322%2FFluid_compute_-_Light_-_Mobile.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F703uGE86SPESaiHPigCGmy%2F5cc98e8b1ab7f04b9013e44fd8251322%2FFluid_compute_-_Light_-_Mobile.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F703uGE86SPESaiHPigCGmy%2F5cc98e8b1ab7f04b9013e44fd8251322%2FFluid_compute_-_Light_-_Mobile.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>AI Gateway</b></a>&nbsp;gives you unified access to hundreds of models with built-in budget control, usage monitoring, and load balancing across providers. This is important for avoiding vendor lock-in and getting instant access to the latest models. When your agent needs to handle different types of queries, AI Gateway can route simple requests to fast, inexpensive models while sending complex analysis to more capable ones. If your primary provider hits rate limits or goes down, traffic automatically fails over to backup providers.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"248\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__desktop rounded-md blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5Ym8tzqsNigo7nUCINxYyu%2F894288009e65c38015788a7077d2cea5%2F1.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5Ym8tzqsNigo7nUCINxYyu%2F894288009e65c38015788a7077d2cea5%2F1.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5Ym8tzqsNigo7nUCINxYyu%2F894288009e65c38015788a7077d2cea5%2F1.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"1546\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__mobile blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5tR8Xf4Pv0Gb3tQQMseU5t%2F7842252a83a69e7758958e34addb6706%2F1-2.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5tR8Xf4Pv0Gb3tQQMseU5t%2F7842252a83a69e7758958e34addb6706%2F1-2.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5tR8Xf4Pv0Gb3tQQMseU5t%2F7842252a83a69e7758958e34addb6706%2F1-2.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://useworkflow.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://useworkflow.dev/\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Workflows</b></a> give agents the ability to perform complex, multi-step operations reliably. When agents are used for critical business processes, failures are costly. Durable orchestration provides retry logic and error handling at every step so that interruptions don't require manual intervention or restart the entire operation.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"397\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__desktop rounded-md blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6sHFohyhYd1hbrUYGM6Bk3%2F64b0af8392be2ef4753d0e8e225ed42d%2FShipeAI25_5-blog-just-ship-agents-light-desktop.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6sHFohyhYd1hbrUYGM6Bk3%2F64b0af8392be2ef4753d0e8e225ed42d%2FShipeAI25_5-blog-just-ship-agents-light-desktop.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F6sHFohyhYd1hbrUYGM6Bk3%2F64b0af8392be2ef4753d0e8e225ed42d%2FShipeAI25_5-blog-just-ship-agents-light-desktop.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"752\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__mobile blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3G4VJbMYENsXA24a7g0r4I%2F7143e973730542b990e832546a7c0cb3%2FShipeAI25_5-blog-just-ship-agents-light-mobile.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3G4VJbMYENsXA24a7g0r4I%2F7143e973730542b990e832546a7c0cb3%2FShipeAI25_5-blog-just-ship-agents-light-mobile.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3G4VJbMYENsXA24a7g0r4I%2F7143e973730542b990e832546a7c0cb3%2FShipeAI25_5-blog-just-ship-agents-light-mobile.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/observability/insights\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/observability/insights\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Observability</b></a> reveals what agents are actually doing beyond basic system metrics. This data is essential for debugging unexpected behavior and optimizing agent performance. When your agent makes unexpected decisions, consumes more tokens than expected, or underperforms, observability shows you the exact prompts, model responses, and decision paths, letting you trace issues back to specific model calls or data sources.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#build-your-agents,-vercel-will-run-them\" id=\"build-your-agents,-vercel-will-run-them\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Build your agents, Vercel will run them</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">In the future, every enterprise will build their version of <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">d0</span>. And their internal code review agent. And their customer support routing agent. And hundreds of other specialized tools.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">The success of these agents depends on the platform that runs them. Companies who invest in their internal AI stack now will not only move faster, they'll experience far higher ROI as their advantages compound over time.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 认为，虽然 AI 降低了智能体原型设计的门槛，但真正的竞争优势在于能够管理生产级安全、可靠性和成本的强大平台。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 认为，虽然 AI 降低了智能体原型设计的门槛，但真正的竞争优势在于能够管理生产级安全、可靠性和成本的强大平台。",
  "summary": "本文探讨了 AI 开发格局的变化，指出虽然得益于 LLM，构建智能体已变得非常简单，但大规模运行它们仍然是一个复杂的工程挑战。文章引入了“内部 AI 技术栈”的概念，这是从“氛围感编程”迈向可靠生产环境的必要条件。Vercel 展示了其智能体编排平台，并以其内部数据智能体 d0 作为主要案例研究。文章详细介绍了特定的基础设施原语——包括用于代码执行的安全沙箱、用于扩展不可预测工作负载的 Fluid Compute、用于模型管理的 AI Gateway 以及用于错误恢复的持久工作流——如何构成了现代智能体架构的基础。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "智能体原型设计已实现普及，但生产部署仍是重大障碍。",
      "explanation": "AI 模型让生成代码变得简单，但大规模管理安全性、可观测性和成本优化需要专门的基础设施，而大多数公司目前仍缺乏这些设施。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“自建还是购买”的投资回报率已转向在托管平台上构建自定义智能体。",
      "explanation": "定制化能为特定工作流带来即时的投资回报，但真正的成本在于长期运行；因此，公司需要一个能自动处理智能体特定需求的平台。"
    },
    {
      "point": "对于生成并运行代码的自主智能体，通过沙箱进行安全执行至关重要。",
      "explanation": "执行敏感操作的智能体需要隔离环境，以防止提示词注入攻击或失控操作损坏核心系统或泄露敏感内部数据。"
    },
    {
      "point": "持久化编排对于处理基于 LLM 的步骤中固有的不稳定性是必要的。",
      "explanation": "由于模型调用可能会失败或超时，工作流必须提供自动重试和状态恢复，以确保业务流程在无需人工干预的情况下完成。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "原型设计已普及，但生产部署并非如此。",
    "竞争优势不再取决于你是否能构建，而在于……能否大规模可靠地运行这些系统。",
    "智能体的终极挑战不在于构建，而在于它们运行的平台。",
    "氛围感编程造成了历史上最大的影子 IT 问题之一。",
    "你构建智能体，Vercel 运行它。一切就是这么简单。"
  ],
